## 🚀 사용 예제

### 1. VQE로 분자 에너지 계산
```javascript
import { VQEOptimizer } from './vqe-solver.js';

const h2o = new MoleculeModel('H2O', [
  { type: 'O', position: [0, 0, 0] },
  { type: 'H', position: [0.96, 0, 0] },
  { type: 'H', position: [-0.24, 0.93, 0] }
]);

const optimizer = new VQEOptimizer(h2o, 2);
const result = optimizer.optimize(50);

console.log(`Ground state energy: ${result.finalEnergy}`);
console.log(`Converged: ${result.converged}`);
```

### 2. QAOA로 MaxCut 문제 해결
```javascript
import { QAOAOptimizer } from './qaoa-optimizer.js';

const problem = new OptimizationProblem('MaxCut',
  [0, 1, 2, 3, 4],
  [[0,1], [1,2], [2,3], [3,4], [4,0], [0,2]]
);

const optimizer = new QAOAOptimizer(problem, 2);
const result = optimizer.optimize(50);

console.log(`Best solution: ${result.bestSolution}`);
console.log(`Approximation ratio: ${result.approximationRatio}`);
```

### 3. 양자 강화학습으로 정책 최적화
```javascript
import { QuantumRLAgent } from './quantum-reinforcement-learning.js';

const agent = new QuantumRLAgent(3, actionSpace);
const result = agent.train(50, 100);

console.log(`Average reward: ${result.averageReward}`);
console.log(`Best reward: ${result.bestReward}`);
```

### 4. 하이브리드 알고리즘 파이프라인
```javascript
import { HybridAlgorithm } from './hybrid-algorithm.js';

const algorithm = new HybridAlgorithm(data);
const result = await algorithm.run(2, true);

console.log(`Success: ${result.success}`);
console.log(`Validity rate: ${result.validation.validityRate}`);
```

